            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1632225196403-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>aubergine slices </strong>to a baking tray (or two!), drizzle each with <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>(save the roughly chopped aubergine for later!)</p><p>Tip: Try to spread the aubergine slices out as much as you can!</p><p>Put the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> in the oven for 18-20 min or until the aubergine slices are tender</p><p>Once cooked, remove from the oven and set aside to cool</p>",
