    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop the <strong>brown onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop the<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>in 200ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [350ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>and add the <strong>dried</strong> <strong>oregano</strong>, <strong>balsamic vinegar </strong>and <strong>tomato paste </strong>– this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse the<strong> cannellini beans</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
