    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain the <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> into rough bite-sized pieces</p><p>Chop the <strong>basil</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p>",
